// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1371 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: d9f37c17-b9c2-5252-b0c9-2cf5b52c6af6

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:17.10*")
